reviews.reviewText: The Dental Guru 3 Pack of toothbrushes, complete with a protective cap, is great to keep handy These toothbrushes prove to be not only soft but also versatile, serving as excellent spare toothbrushes, ideal for travel, and perfect for guests. The soft bristles provide a gentle yet effective cleaning experience, making them a reliable choice for maintaining oral hygiene.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good value for the price
reviews.reviewText: I like that for such a cheap price I get three at once! Comfy handle, sufficiently soft bristles. I like the caps too, they have holes for ventilation to prevent mold growth. Only issue I've had is toothpaste residue on the caps but for the most part that can be fixed by rinsing the caps.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Not battery powered idk why it says that
reviews.reviewText: I got these because I need a new set and they say they are soft but they are definitely a medium almost hard. All in all it's been a good toothbrush no bristles breaking or falling out just not exactly what the description says it is.

reviews.reviewText: So honestly, no one is going to complain too loudly about 3 toothbrushes for $1.60, but they are not battery powered. They're just normal, run of the mill toothbrushes like what a dentist would give you on the way out the door.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars NOT BATTERY! FALSE ADVERTISING!
reviews.reviewText: It says over 3xs in description BATTERY POWERED & it even says under components included: BATTERY! I wondered why so cheap, that's the only reason I bought these. They are just plain old dumb toothbrushes & don't even have the rubber side teeth most have. You can get a 6 pack of better brushes for $1 from elsewhere! I'm keeping them cause was only $1.60 & I'll use them for cleaning my mini vacuum filter or jobs where need to get in tight places,but I can get 6 for less! Change the description!
